summary: Alternative Grey Wolf (edited from Bellyache´s Retextured Wolves)
descriptionHtml:
===================================================================================
This mod based on the Retextured Wolves and Pelts by Bellyache which you can found here:

http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1292
===================================================================================

This is my alternative version of a grey wolf instead for the original black wolf. 

Simply copy the extracted data folder in your Skyryím Folder.

- fixed mouth, teeth, tonque and eye color
